title: Watch Out, There's A Flying Pig! (Pink Floyd Bootleg)
description:
From a Pink Floyd Bootleg-CD called "Watch Out, There's A Flying Pig", released by pablo records.

Tracks 1-5 recorded live at Pavillion de Paris, France, February 25, 1977.
1. Shine On You Crazy Diamond (Parts 1-5)
2. Welcome To The Machine
3. Have A  Cigar
4. Wish You Were Here
5. Shine On You Crazy Diamond (Parts 6-9)

Track 6 is the studio recordings of Pigs On The Wing, parts 1 and 2, abridged by a guitarsolo from Snowy White.
